<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen will capture AFMSF-7A case sheet details. User can write patient complaints, patient history, patient examinations, patient clinical details, patient diagnosis, Drugs details, investigation details, patient plan and patient next patient visit date. OPD Patient AFMSF-7A screen is common for all departments.
